latestIgtvVideos.title: The Assamdowntownuniversity @assamdowntownuniversity
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I am very delighted to share with all the young people of the state, especially the ones who are interested in pursuing professional careers in dance, music and drama that now you can go for a Performing Arts degree course affordably and comfortably in our neighbouring state of Assam. I understand that many parents are worried about sending their children far away after the Pandemic hit us but with @AssamdowntownUniversity there is nothing to worry about. The university offers a wide range of 64 programmes in different disciplines of Engineering, Management, Nursing, Paramedics, Hospitality, Humanities, Social Sciences and Pharmacy to more than 8000 plus students with over 250 plus faculty members. 

You get quality education at an affordable cost for the people of the North-eastern Region of India with world-class facilities and great placement records. I am so happy to see such highly recognized, top-ranked and culturally diverse universities coming up in North-East states with even students from abroad opting to study here. Why think twice when you have the best right in front of you? To know more click on the link on my bio and know more about AdtU now.
